{"id":838,"date":"2017-03-15T20:21:34","date_gmt":"2017-03-15T20:21:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=838"},"modified":"2024-05-27T20:12:59","modified_gmt":"2024-05-27T20:12:59","slug":"mollie","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/mollie\/","title":{"rendered":"Mollie"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Offer your customers the payment methods Creditcard, SOFORT Banking, iDEAL, Bancontact, Bank transfer, SEPA Direct Debit, PayPal, Bitcoin, PODIUM Cadeaukaart, Paysafecard, or Belfius Direct Net. Mollie is known for reliability, transparency.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mollie handles the payment processing for you, <strong>no SSL certificate<\/strong> is required on your site, and you don\u2019t have to worry about PCI compliance. Customers select their favorite payment method at checkout and are redirected to Mollie or their bank\u2019s site to finish the payment process. You benefit from easy, <strong>secure<\/strong> payment processing, and <strong>improve customer satisfaction<\/strong> by offering multiple payment methods.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Setup and configuration<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>To set up the Mollie payment gateway you will need&nbsp;to login into your Mollie account and obtain API Key (<a href=\"https:\/\/mollie.com\">sign up<\/a> if you don&#8217;t have one).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Go to your&nbsp;Mollie dashboard navigate to <strong>Developers-&gt;API Keys<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"888\" height=\"702\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/VaBeBUy.png\" alt=\"Mollie Developers Menu Item\" class=\"wp-image-4357\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/VaBeBUy.png 888w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/VaBeBUy-300x237.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/VaBeBUy-768x607.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/VaBeBUy-60x47.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/VaBeBUy-150x119.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 888px) 100vw, 888px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>Based on your website profiles, and the profile you want to use, <strong>copy the API key<\/strong> that you are going to use for your Perfex CRM installation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You will see two sections for the API keys, a <em>live<\/em> API key and a <em>test<\/em> API key, Live API key will be visible once your website profile has been verified by the team at Mollie (if not yet verfied).<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert- \"><strong>NOTE<\/strong>: For testing use the Test API Key,\u00a0for production you will need to use the Live\u00a0API Key<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>After everything is set up well in your Mollie dashboard, in Perfex CRM go to <strong>Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;Payment Gateways<\/strong> and click on the <strong>Mollie<\/strong> tab, <strong>paste your API key and&nbsp;save the settings.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert-danger \"><\/strong>When using test api key you need to enable test mode.<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mod Security<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If using, contact your hosting and ask them to<strong> disable mod_security for your Perfex CRM installation<\/strong> because in certain scenarios ModSecurity will interfere with the webhook and may block the request which will lead to<strong> invoice status not updating.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Testing<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>After you entered the <strong>test Mollie API Key,<\/strong> you can perform the following steps:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Create a dummy customer.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Create an invoice under the customer you created before and in the <strong>Allowed Payment Modes<\/strong> make sure that you select <strong>Mollie<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>View the invoice as a customer, while previewing the invoice in the admin area click <strong>More-&gt;View Invoice as Customer<\/strong>.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scroll to the bottom and select <strong>Mollie <\/strong>and click <strong>Pay Now<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Offer your customers the payment methods Creditcard, SOFORT Banking, iDEAL, Bancontact, Bank transfer, SEPA Direct Debit, PayPal, Bitcoin, PODIUM Cadeaukaart, Paysafecard, or Belfius Direct Net. Mollie is known for reliability, transparency. Mollie handles the payment processing for you, no SSL certificate is required on your site, and you don\u2019t have to worry about PCI compliance. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-838","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-payment-gateways"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/838","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=838"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/838\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=838"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=838"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=838"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","